      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> roughly</p><p>Tip: Slice into rings for speedy chopping!</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a very high heat</p>",
