      "instruction": "<p>Once very hot, add the <strong>beef strips</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until browned all over</p><p>Transfer the <strong>beef strips</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: Don't worry if the beef strips aren't fully cooked through yet, they'll go back in the pan later!</p>",
